{"id": 130, "genre": 1000, "title": "办公室零食，你偏爱哪一种？", "description": "在办公室吃东西最重要的是什么？是找到一种小小的、适口的、吃起来没声音的、又带一点刺激感觉的食物，趁老板同事不注意塞到嘴里吃掉，啊哈，心中充满了愉悦。（所在公司气氛宽松可以随便吃零食的朋友们请主动忽略这道题不要给人添堵谢谢）\r\n", "record_count": 3085, "comment_count": 42, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/2016070218371968C7le0tWf1XYoFn.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2014-11-04T08:52:19Z", "questions": [{"id": 116, "title": "办公室零食，你偏爱哪一种？", "content": "办公室零食，你偏爱哪一种？\r\n", "genre": 1, "options": [{"id": 985, "content": "膨化食品", "image": "img/option/option/201606071925339dvaHAPgSB7C5NxJ.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 986, "content": "糖", "image": "img/option/option/2016060719253348rMbZ7nUJX09hCu.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 987, "content": "巧克力", "image": "img/option/option/20160607193158QrFDtkBmw1xWUyVu.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 988, "content": "肉干、肉松、肉脯类", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182722WBQm4NZjqnMkRzCi.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 989, "content": "坚果、炒货", "image": "img/option/option/20160702182840tRU1OMsJdBNWuQx4.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 990, "content": "酸奶", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192534H1u9A3f4j67mpFzE.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 991, "content": "糕点、饼干", "image": "img/option/option/20160702183017H07uhl6xjvMeCNbq.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 992, "content": "说啥呢，我才不爱吃零食", "image": "img/option/option/20160607192534y3ZULj0cN1t9q4sl.jpg", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}